==English==

===Proper noun===
'''Negro''' plural negros, negroes (Often capitalized) 
#''Archaic.'' A person of [[sub-Saharan]] [[African]] descent; [[black]].

====Derived terms====
*[[negress]] / [[Negress]]
*[[negroid]] / [[Negroid]]

